---
// MarketIntel.astro — inteligencia de mercado (card destacada, parte alta del home)
---
<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-12 sm:px-8">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-navy-deep px-7 py-8 ring-1 ring-teal/25 sm:px-9 sm:py-9" data-reveal>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-16 -top-16 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-teal/15 blur-3xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative grid items-center gap-6 sm:grid-cols-[auto_1fr_auto]">
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal/20 text-teal">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <!-- Text -->
        <div>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-teal/20 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal ring-1 ring-teal/30">Plan Enterprise</span>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-extrabold text-white sm:text-xl">Inteligencia de mercado, incluida</h3>
          <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
            Antes de presentar, sabe <strong class="text-white">quién ganó procesos similares</strong>, a qué precio
            ofertaron y con qué historial de adjudicaciones. Preparas tu propuesta con argumento de precio, no a ciegas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- CTA -->
        <a href="/precios" class="hidden shrink-0 items-center rounded-xl bg-teal px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg transition hover:bg-teal/90 sm:inline-flex whitespace-nowrap">
          Ver Enterprise →
        </a>
      </div>
      <!-- Mobile CTA -->
      <div class="relative mt-4 sm:hidden">
        <a href="/precios" class="text-sm font-bold text-teal hover:text-teal/80 transition">Ver Enterprise →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
